snippet.title: Rakht Charitra 1 Full Hindi Movie | Vivek Oberoi, Radhika Apte, Sudeep | Ram Gopal Varma Movies
snippet.description:
Enjoy the Bollywood Super hit action Hindi movie "Rakht Charitra 1", starring Vivek Oberoi, Radhika Apte, Shatrughan Sinha, Kota Srinivasa Rao, Zarina Wahab, Sudeep, Sushmita Mukherjee, Sushant Singh, Ashish Vidyarthi & Others. Music By Sukhwinder Singh. Directed by Ram Gopal Varma and produced by Cinergy.
#RamGopalVarmaMovies #RadhikaApteMovies #VivekOberoiMovies

Movie: Rakht Charitra 1 (2010)
Music: Sukhwinder Singh
Producer: Rajkumar Akella, Madhu Mantena, Chinna Vasudeva Reddy & Sheetal Vinod Talwar
Star Cast: Vivek Oberoi, Radhika Apte, Shatrughan Sinha, Sudeep, Zarina Wahab, Sushant Singh & Others.

Synopsis: 
Rakta Charitra is a biographical tale of Paritala Ravi from Andhra Pradesh, a prime accused in a number of murder cases. It is the story of a man's phenomenal rise to power and a story of the most intense blood curdling conflict ever heard of between two individuals. Moreover, the story is also the ultimate statement on the often heard disastrous consequences of a fatal mixture of caste, crime, family feuds and politics.
